  <brief_title>The Influence of Peripheral Nerve Blocks in Patients Undergoing Limb Orthopedic Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preoperative Peripheral Nerve Blocks Attenuate Intraoperative Surgical Stress and Postoperative Pain in Patients Undergoing Orthopedic Surgery</official_title>
